#* {{quote-book|year=1386|author={{w|Geoffrey Chaucer}}|title=The Canon's Yeoman's Tale|chapter=Line 881|edition=|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=vABEAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA556|passage=Whicħ þat þey myght / wrape hem in at nyght / And a '''brat''' / to walk in / by day-light}}
