#* {{quote-book|year=1882|author=John Strathesk|title=Blinkbonny|chapter=pp. 135|edition=|url=[http://books.google.com/books?id=ga0yAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA382 The English Dialect Dictionary... ''brat'']|passage=[She] had still on the rough worsted apron of nappy homespun wool, called a '''"brat"'''.}}
